 {"id":"frankenredis-slex","title":"Add stateful fuzz target for fr-store streams and consumer groups","description":"Evidence: existing fuzz_runtime_sequence only covers basic string/list/set/hash/zset/key/db commands in fuzz/fuzz_targets/fuzz_runtime_sequence.rs, but it never exercises stream or consumer-group state. High-risk uncovered entry points live in crates/fr-store/src/lib.rs:6609 (xadd), 6873 (xread), 6906 (xreadgroup), 7367 (xgroup_create), 7412 (xgroup_destroy), 7443 (xgroup_setid), 7505 (xgroup_createconsumer), and 7584 (xgroup_delconsumer).\\n\\nNeed: add a structure-aware/stateful libFuzzer target under fuzz/fuzz_targets/ that drives stream IDs, pending entries, consumer creation/deletion, and readgroup ack-like progress through a shadow model or invariant suite (no duplicate delivery regressions, pending counts stay nonnegative, failed ops do not mutate unrelated state, dump/restore preserves stream-group metadata).\\n\\nReal impl path: fuzz/Cargo.toml plus new fuzz/fuzz_targets/fuzz_store_stream_groups.rs targeting the fr-store stream/group APIs directly.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-04-22T17:47:47.378853544Z","created_by":"cod-redis","updated_at":"2026-04-22T19:23:41.677946988Z","closed_at":"2026-04-22T19:23:41.676033426Z","close_reason":"Completed","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["fr-store","fuzz","testing"]}
